wer and practical utility: it reveals whether bias stems from shallow heuristics or deep contextual integration, informs targeted debiasing strategies, and provides a generalizable tool for auditing other identity-based biases (e.g., gender, ethnicity). If successful, this work will advance the field by shifting bias analysis from outcome-level statistics to mechanistic interpretability, enabling more precise and effective fairness interventions.",
